Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.25,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}FLYING IN THE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:09.19,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最高的地方 馳騁於空中的任何角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.92,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮大地的盡頭呼喚奇跡的咒語 {\fnComic Sans MS}SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:25.44,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不遲疑的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:31.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有無限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:39.08,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論嘗試多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:47.51,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼痛苦都貫徹到底{\fnComic Sans MS}（G GUNDAM）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:50.63,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛隨時都充斥於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.21,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:57.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手 咆哮著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.31,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向明天飛奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.10,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}BRIGHT YOU NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所描繪的未來之藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.80,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.34,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部如你所願 {\fnComic Sans MS}I GET A CHANCE！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來，60年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從人類移居宇宙衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都也變成現在這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此，如果不奉杯茶給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會受到懲罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想不到你們會相約在這種
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極度荒廢的寺院內見面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來早了一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，反正莉茵小姐不會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是什麼人…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日終於要講關於這照片的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這男人究竟是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休為何要追捕這男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上最強的Devil Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會告訴我們所有答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56}戰鬥吧多蒙！地球就是擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一小隊，第二小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責A至F區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三至第五小隊堅守G至L區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它現身的一剎那是唯一的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定要命中目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,De…Devil Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是一年前的事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，這一帶終於也重建了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有任何痕跡留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事的確不可給其他衛星國家知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可因此便利用GUNDAM FIGHT啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，卡敕度委員長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，請看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙很快便會醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，他將會看見的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是當日他從漫長的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武術修練旅程回到這裡後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來了，喂，你要睡到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是哥哥嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你強壯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…真的很久沒見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！？媽媽！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了飯沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我回來了，爸爸，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？烏爾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎，大賽舉行期間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落地球的成員不可回到衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不同意這項檢測值得你\N不惜觸犯GUNDAM FIGHT的國際條約
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的擔心很有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那能證明那個多蒙·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:06:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是解決這件事的最佳人選
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不見了，多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎！？那是你修練武術前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常一起玩的莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她漂亮了，令你嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的確離開了這個家十年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我在那期間得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個King Of Heart的稱號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，原來我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為衛星格鬥技的霸主嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的師傅叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Asia，他很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他在衛星格鬥技五天王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒夫爾同盟中是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱東方不敗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是前任King Of Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他突然把這稱號讓給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後便不知所蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那些，多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和我也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之，那個…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間的話，待會讓你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西何時看也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日是多蒙從修練旅程回來的慶祝會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別提工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則，當時的事又會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽弄的畢竟是最好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你便一直留在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又出門的話，我會很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心，我不會再離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人一起生活畢竟是最幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你修練時也非常懷念媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，我已經不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在媽媽我眼中你還是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過份…怎樣也好，太過份了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對幻覺的深層心理測試結果很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只靠這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam很快會像當日一樣出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何擅自離開那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，我不想再做戲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣也好，多蒙這樣很可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也說不上是一種刑罰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！？多蒙什麼也沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎，我們無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要多蒙繼續參加GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，卡敕度委員長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不理會地球現在有何危機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只管想著勝出FIGHT回去領功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後得到新日本的首相寶座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵，跟著是測驗的最重要的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我擔心,卡敕度有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和京二造出來的GUNDAM如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，這部GUNDAM關係人類的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，它關係人類的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了這一部GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會變得有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡休博士，還有京二·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以叛國罪逮捕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，究竟是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們企圖利用那部完成了的GUNDAM作為武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞這個宇宙的衛星聯邦和地球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後支配全人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直混帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的行動出奇地快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位軍警先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙，他們的話沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…認真的嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這部GUNDAM已經任由我控制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京二！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京二！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止！我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京二，這是誤會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京二…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！媽媽她…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助記錄造出來的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他當時是不在現場的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙就像是時空交錯回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，竟然變成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身為你爸爸的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在十分難過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:13:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新日本政府把你爸爸當作同謀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判處永久冷凍刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經努力替他辯護
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但極其量只能免他被判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而Devil Gundam就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落在地球的某國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多厲害也好，當時下降速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不會安然無恙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情以為告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那只不過是開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過進一步的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發現一件不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，即是它在沖人大氣層時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損毀再嚴重也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它擁有的自我增殖，自我再生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及自我進化這三大理論機能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾令它再次重生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而京二·卡休一定會發揮其能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在地球的統治權在新香港手上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你成為Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我的計算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在地球完全再生須時一年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，那一年恰好舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年一度的GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時，你就能在地球自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你利用那機會捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則，一切都會變成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能捉住它的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有身為King Of Heart的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把…哥哥…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡敕度委員長！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做有什麼作用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要勝出擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也需要他的強大意志力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，他一直以來戰績不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因何在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Maxter，Dragon Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Rose，Bolt Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾經白白放過取勝的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為比賽後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道他們和他的哥哥京二無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，指示多蒙和他們比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我們希望他先查探
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信已經知道Devil Gundam一事的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，結果適得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們承認失敗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，這次測驗就用我的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來找出答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他面對哥哥時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是否真的能打倒哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是否能把親兄弟當作敵人作出攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來實驗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然這是實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休操縱真正的Shining Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而對手就是MA：Fantoma
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，幻覺會令他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看見真正的Devil Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為實驗，這不太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們放心，多蒙有什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會以我的權力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令國際委員會破例批准更換Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對那對手，他能戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時只懂發抖，毫無還手之力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而Fantoma的嚴重損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使你帶上了這個面具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然有所圖謀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，你睡一會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙，現在還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開Shining Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要攻擊哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決他吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及時趕到，但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救護組！快救我女兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUN…GUNDAM在發光！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！不，京二！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會饒恕你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你令媽媽慘死，令爸爸蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會放過你！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56\pos(512,348)}Super Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56\pos(512,568)}Shining Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我們Shining Gundam的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真面目！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，當他的怒火達到頂點時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的感情會化成能量令GUNDAM變型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以致能發揮最大的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之，真正能運用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們Shining Gundam的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有立誓要向哥哥報仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這隻手在閃耀和咆哮！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在叫我打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是包含了愛、憤怒和悲傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SWORD！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡敕度？聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再用這種技倆！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！你什麼時候從幻覺裡…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著！你們今後乖乖做個旁觀者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會捉住京二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手打倒Devil Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後隨便他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵，我們返回地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，應該說返回擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次雖然很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，就算有任何障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不能不管那部Devil Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:22:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，令千金也會遇上悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我們會同心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一日來臨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要成為不懼悲痛的孤獨戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:31.50,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便數千的日夜流逝
